text:
Hello Everyone, Discover how Speedy can transform the tough job of back-end API development into fun and blazing fast. In other words, Speedy is 'Productivity on Steroids' for API/back-end development.

Speedy enables you to Author RESTful Endpoints, Key-Value storage, and JS-based Functions in minutes, confidently. Save BIG on development time, hosting expenses, service scale-out, service downtime, and maintenance.

We would be happy to receive your feedback, comments and feature requests. Please do not hesitate to reach us at support@getspeedy.app for anything.

To know more please do visit http://www.getspeedy.app.

Regards, Team Speedy
